# .terraformignore — controls what files HCP Terraform uploads from the repo root.
# The HCP workspace is configured to use EmailNotionSync.Terraform/azure/ as its
# working directory, but it uploads the full repo context.  Exclude large or
# irrelevant directories to keep uploads fast.

# .NET build outputs
**/bin/
**/obj/

# NuGet packages
**/packages/

# Test results
**/*.trx
**/TestResults/

# IDE / OS
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Secrets / local overrides (never upload)
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/terraform.tfvars.backup

# Git internals
**/.git/
